details.sectionContent: Participating students will be taught how to make a RC Plane.

Day 1:
‣	Styrofoam sheet with the dimensioning and shape of each part will be provided.
‣	Participant will have to cut out the parts from Styrofoam and assemble them to form the model.
	Participants will recieve help by the volunteers to do the same.

Day-2:-
‣	The model will be facilitated with servo motors, receiver, battery and main engine. Flight test will be conducted for each model.
Civil Seminar Hall on 5th Feb @ 10:45 am
